TITLE: Claim Function Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Allows claiming multiple lazy minted NFTs to a recipient with reentrancy protection and custom verification logic.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/contracts/build/base-contracts/erc-1155/lazy-mint/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
