TITLE: Execute Batch Transactions Function
DESCRIPTION: Function to execute multiple transactions in sequence, callable only by admin or entrypoint.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/contracts/build/extensions/erc-4337/AccountExtension/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
function executeBatch(
    address[] calldata _target,
    uint256[] calldata _value,
    bytes[] calldata _calldata
) external virtual onlyAdminOrEntrypoint {
    require(_target.length == _calldata.length && _target.length == _value.length, "Account: wrong array lengths.");
    for (uint256 i = 0; i < _target.length; i++) {
        _call(_target[i], _value[i], _calldata[i]);
    }
}
```

