TITLE: Implementing thirdweb Auth with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet shows the full auth flow using TypeScript, including initializing the client, generating a login payload, signing the payload on the client, verifying signatures, generating JWTs, and authenticating subsequent requests. It demonstrates the server-side and client-side components of the authentication process.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/connect/auth/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: ts
