TITLE: Internal Call Function
DESCRIPTION: Internal function to make contract calls and handle reverts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/contracts/build/extensions/erc-4337/AccountExtension/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
function _call(
    address _target,
    uint256 value,
    bytes memory _calldata
) internal {
    (bool success, bytes memory result) = _target.call{ value: value }(_calldata);
    if (!success) {
        assembly {
            revert(add(result, 32), mload(result))
        }
    }
}
```

