TITLE: Restricted Payload Authentication Example
DESCRIPTION: Advanced example showing how to restrict an access token to a specific payload using SHA256 hashing
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/engine/features/keypair-authentication/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_6

LANGUAGE: typescript
