TITLE: Signature Minting Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Core function for minting tokens using signature verification. Processes the mint request, collects payment, and mints tokens to the specified receiver.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/contracts/build/base-contracts/erc-20/signature-mint/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
/**
 *  @notice           Mints tokens according to the provided mint request.
 *
 *  @param _req       The payload / mint request.
 *  @param _signature The signature produced by an account signing the mint request.
 */
function mintWithSignature(MintRequest calldata _req, bytes calldata _signature)
    external
    payable
    virtual
    returns (address signer)
{
    require(_req.quantity > 0, "Minting zero tokens.");

    // Verify and process payload.
    signer = _processRequest(_req, _signature);

    address receiver = _req.to;

    // Collect price
    _collectPriceOnClaim(_req.primarySaleRecipient, _req.quantity, _req.currency, _req.pricePerToken);

    // Mint tokens.
    _mint(receiver, _req.quantity);

    emit TokensMintedWithSignature(signer, receiver, _req);
}
```

