SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/contracts/build/base-contracts/erc-721/delayed-reveal/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: solidity
CODE:
```
function reveal(uint256 _index, bytes calldata _key) external virtual override returns (string memory revealedURI) {
    require(_canReveal(), "Not authorized");

    uint256 batchId = getBatchIdAtIndex(_index);
    revealedURI = getRevealURI(batchId, _key);

    _setEncryptedData(batchId, "");
    _setBaseURI(batchId, revealedURI);

    emit TokenURIRevealed(_index, revealedURI);
}
```

