TITLE: Converting v4 Signer to v5 Account in React
DESCRIPTION: Demonstrates how to obtain the current signer using the useSigner hook from v4 and convert it for use with the new SDK v5.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/typescript/v5/migrate/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { useSigner } from "@thirdweb-dev/react";
import { ethers5Adapter } from "thirdweb/adapters/ethers5";

const signer = useSigner();

const onClick = async () => {
    // convert the signer to used with the new SDK
	const account = await ethers5Adapter.signer.fromEthers(signer);
    // then use the new SDK normally
    const transaction = prepareContractCall({ ... });
    await sendTransaction({
	    transaction,
	    account,
    });
};
```

