DESCRIPTION: This code creates metadata for the documentation page, including the title, description, and image information. It uses the createMetadata function, likely a custom utility for generating consistent metadata across documentation pages.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/account/billing/upgrade-plan/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
export const metadata = createMetadata({
	title: "Billing & Plan Upgrades",
	description: "Learn how to upgrade your thirdweb plan",
	image: {
		title: "Billing & Plan Upgrades",
		icon: "thirdweb",
	},
});
```

