TITLE: Defining Metadata for Drop Contract Documentation in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet creates metadata for the Drop contract design document, including the title, description, and image information. It uses the createMetadata function from a custom module.
SOURCE: https://github.com/thirdweb-dev/js/blob/main/apps/portal/src/app/contracts/design-docs/drop/page.mdx#2025-04-14_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
export const metadata = createMetadata({
	image: {
		title: "Drop contract design document",
		icon: "contract",
	},
	title: "Drop contract design document | thirdweb",
	description:
		"This is a live document that explains what the thirdweb Drop smart contracts are, how they work and can be used, and why they are written the way they are",
});
```
